

# See http://www.bobotig.fr/contenu/documents/guide-pombo
# for more informations.


*** All
    - One or more distants servers where to put encrypted files

*** Windows
    - (*) GnuPT (or GnuPG4Win)

*** GNU/Linux
    - python
    - python-ipy
    - python-requests
    - (*) GnuPG
    - iw
    - traceroute
    - scrot
    - streamer
    All of these tools should be into your repositories:
        Debian based: aptitude install python python-ipy python-requests gnupg net-tools iw traceroute scrot streamer

*** Mac
    - python-ipy
    - python-requests
    To install these modules: sudo easy_install requests ipy
    - (*) GnuPG: https://gpgtools.org/
    - ImageSnap: http://iharder.sourceforge.net/current/macosx/imagesnap/


(*) Not necessary if encryption is disabled, which is not recommended.
